Algorithm

Prompt user for- “Would you like to continue?”
Get input from user
Check for three things: -
1.	If user prompts “Yes”-Continue –Re-Prompt the user
2.	If user prompts “other” –Display error message”- “re-Prompt the user”
3.	If user prompts “No”-Quit


Pseudocode
step 1: Initialize an empty string. (say str)
step 2: Construct a new “Scanner” object
Step 3: prompt the user
Step 4: Get the user input
Step 5: while user prompts yes
	Input the next line
	If responses no
	System quits
	else
	Display error message and re-prompts again
	End if
End while
